results.description:
En route to Serengeti National Park, we found this gazelle. Gazelles are not so common to find in India. Or at least not in the cities. :)

We stopped to take a few snaps of this gazelle. Turns out we were going to see a lot of gazelles of different types during our time in Serengeti!
